ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Why is the history of God&apos;s people so important for me to know? </div><div class="t m21 x56 h23 y1e4 ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m1b1 x2b h23 ya9b ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Why is it important that I take every opportunity to tell people how </div><div class="t m392 xd h23 yb77 ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">grateful I am for what God has done for me? </div><div class="t m58c x79 h4d yb78 ff1 fs25 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In</div><div class="t m28f x6a h24 y191 ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FURTHER STUDY AND MEDITATION: </div><div class="t m1a1 xbb h23 y191 ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Read </div><div class="t m20d x92 h23 y2c3 ff9 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Testimonies, vol. </div><div class="t m507 xa2 h23 y2c3 ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5, pp. </div><div class="t m349 x6a h23 y192 ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">315-319. </div><div class="t m1c7 x6a h24 y238 ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: </div><div class="t m29f xbc h23 y194 ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The psalmist urges us to raise our voices in thanksgiving to </div><div class="t m1ce x6a h23 yb79 ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God. Ellen White wrote, &quot;As Christians we ought to praise God more than </div><div class="t m201 x6a h23 y196 ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we do. We ought to bring more of the brightness of His love into our </div><div class="t mc2 x6a h23 yb7a ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lives.&quot;—Ellen G. White Comments, </div><div class="t m8c xaf h23 y197 ff9 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SDA Bible Commentary, </div><div class="t m9b x83 h23 y197 ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 1148. The </div><div class="t m221 x6a h23 y23a ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">psalmist testifies to God&apos;s goodness in answering prayers. What holds us </div><div class="t m149 x6a h23 y19a ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">back from praising God in every situation of life? </div><div class="t m347 x6a h24 y1ab ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">96 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></